des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : appdeveloper@haneco.com.au

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 

After connecting Alexa to your Kasta Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "KASTA" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Kasta Smart account in our "KASTA" app;
(3). You need to have some Kasta Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our KASTA app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Kasta Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Katsa Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Kasta Smart", and you'll be navigated to Kasta login page;
(9). Input your Kasta account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
